IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GRPDEMO.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 SRC-REC.
   05 S-NAME PIC X(8) VALUE "WIDGET".
   05 S-QTY  PIC 9(3) VALUE 42.
01 DST-REC.
   05 D-NAME PIC X(8).
   05 D-QTY  PIC 9(3).
01 CODE-X PIC X(10) VALUE "ABCDEFGHIJ".
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE SRC-REC TO DST-REC.
    DISPLAY "Dst name: " D-NAME " qty: " D-QTY.
    MOVE "XYZ" TO CODE-X(2:3).
    DISPLAY "Code: " CODE-X.
    STOP RUN.
